com.legacy.structure_gel.util

Class GelPortalSize

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.legacy.structure_gel.util.GelPortalSize

  • public class GelPortalSize
extends java.lang.Object
    A version of PortalSize to work with GelPortalBlock and GelTeleporter. Call isValidSize() to check if you're in a portal frame or trySpawnPortal(IWorld, BlockPos, GelPortalBlock, List) to attempt to spawn a portal at the position.
    Author:
    David
